<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.179669>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1 – 7. Male terminalia of Swammerdamellini genera. 1 – 3. Pararhexosa chelata (Cook), 1971. Male paratype (1, ventral; 2, lateral, 3, dorsal). 4 – 5. Rhexoza subnitens (Verrall). 6 – 7. Akorhexoza sp. 1 (4, ventral, 5, dorsal)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/179669/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

